The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Ismael Cruz, Appellant.

Supreme Court, Bronx County, rendered on September 21, 1977, unanimously affirmed. The order of this court entered on April 24, 1979 is vacated. No opinion. Concur—Fein, J. P., Sullivan, Lane, Lupiano and Ross, JJ.
